FeedPackage.Description:
MagneticPdf offers a reliable, multi-threaded html to pdf conversion. Capable of converting HTML from strings, files, streams, and URLs, MagneticPdf enables you to easily transform web based content to high-quality, standards-compliant PDF output.
The MagneticPdf SDK offers full support for HTML tags, CSS styles, page breaks control with CSS styles.
It also supports live URLs and internal links in PDF, bookmarks, HTML in the headers and footers, unicode, right to left text and many more.
FeedPackage.Summary: MagneticPdf offers a powerful, yet easy to use .NET library that can convert html to pdf on the fly.
FeedPackage.Tags: html-to-pdf pdf-generation pdf html-to-pdf-converter converter
FeedPackage.Title: MagneticPdf
